### 1. Create a New Category
POST http://localhost:4015/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics",
  "description": "Electronic gadgets and devices"
}

### 2. Get All Categories
GET http://localhost:4015/api/categories

### 3. Get Category by ID (Ganti ID sesuai dengan hasil create)
GET http://localhost:4015/api/categories/1

### 4. Update Category (Ganti ID sesuai kebutuhan)
PATCH http://localhost:4015/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Consumer Electronics",
  "description": "Updated description for electronics"
}

### 5. Delete Category (Ganti ID sesuai kebutuhan)
DELETE http://localhost:4015/api/categories/1
